    "• The first version of our algorithm, JUMP*, outperforms the baselines in the absence of perplexity control.",
    "• We recognize the trade-off between ASRs and perplexity and observe that a well-chosen initial seed set can mitigate it.",
    "Our experiments show that with carefully designed initial prompts, the enhanced version of our method, JUMP++, significantly outperforms state-ofthe-art methods in the universal attack setting.",
    "• We adapt our attack algorithm for defense.",
